                  <p class="p">Picking the right Hiking Gear!</p>
                  <p class="text-wrapper-6">
                    The nice thing about beginning hiking is that you don’t really need any special gear, you can
                    probably get away with things you already have.<br />Let’s start with clothing. A typical mistake
